00:32:31.400 --> 00:32:32.040
Xiguang

00:32:32.420 --> 00:32:33.420
sagutin mo ako.

00:32:34.800 --> 00:32:35.520
Siya ba

00:32:36.420 --> 00:32:37.840
humahabol sa iyo?

