pero talagang namukod-tangi sila

00:34:43.199 --> 00:34:44.179
sa karamihan.

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:46.080
Nie Chengyuan.

00:34:47.060 --> 00:34:48.159
Pangalan niya iyon, 'di ba?

