Hindi ako masyadong humanga.

00:34:57.360 --> 00:34:58.340
Sa kabilang banda, si Jiang Yun

00:34:58.560 --> 00:35:00.880
nagkaroon ng kalmado at mahinahong hangin,

00:35:01.340 --> 00:35:02.420
perpektong nakaayos.

00:35:02.960 --> 00:35:03.820
Hindi ako nakatulong

00:35:04.000 --> 00:35:04.940
